gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔接機 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔衝禁區<br />\n<br />\n保持憤怒 統一口號<br />\n「黑警還眼」<br />\n「五大訴求，缺一不可」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4052749f0a52a9cde03eb8804fb2646111ca76be","tid":1451164,"uid":84657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:28:59.000Z","msg":"811<br />\n1. 尖沙咀瞄頭射，射爆女仕眼球<br />\n2. 以化學武器攻擊葵芳/太古車站內<br />\n3. 北角無視黑幫攻擊記者/平民<br />\n4. 非公職時參與非法集會，以磚/汽油彈攻擊防暴警犬，煽動民眾<br />\n5. 製造偽証"},{"pid":"d3aa797125a01afc262ee2ed28af513b71bb3ffe","tid":1451164,"uid":264717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:29:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5322bb0a8d8cc0863f48a50897b1afb6514de208","tid":1451164,"uid":25640,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:29:25.000Z","msg":"雖然唔鐘意民陣 亦唔覺得佢係大台<br />\n但無可否認民陣叫到最多人 大家都會留力去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"534f0018123dcd066b84f894343c526f13f91764","tid":1451164,"uid":259622,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:29:32.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n而家成個運動會好似係變左同班狗玩捉兒因咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我和理非表示已經睇唔到啲衝突究竟係有咩意義...<br />\n可唔可以正正常常搞多一次遊行叫林鄭落台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />推政改推普選<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60d74f0aab68d02e705c739c658418b9ced111c3","tid":1451164,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0520ad020fbfc2dc35823519c5fb52c8bee0cea7","tid":1451164,"uid":25640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:27:06.000Z","msg":"依加大家咁憤怒<br />\n個人認為民陣應該盡快搞遊行<br />\n聚一聚氣 向政府表達我地既不滿<